These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, time-travel, scientific, crime, epic, western, comedy
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, woodworking, magic-tricks, gardening, singing, collecting
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | crime | time-travel | scientific | zombie | western | comedy |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | gardening   | magic-tricks      | singing | woodworking    | rock-climbing    | collecting         |

