 3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
