The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving, collecting, puzzles, sudoku, cooking
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Cigar    | chaman | bluemaster   | bolivar | baccarat | aristoff  | swisher | pall-mall |
| Hobby   | collecting   | puzzles | camping | sudoku     | card-games | cooking | skydiving   |

