 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the ranch-style house is the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the craftsman house is in the middle##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

